stash - Bidirectionally sync Markdown files with Apple Notes

Usage:
  stash COMMAND
  stash [COMMAND] --help | -h
  stash --version | -v

Commands:
  push          Push a Markdown file or directory to Apple Notes (create or update)
  pull          Pull content from Apple Notes to a Markdown file or directory
  diff          Show differences between a Markdown file and its linked Apple Note
  sync          Two-way sync a Markdown file or directory with Apple Notes
  completions   Generate bash completions

Options:
  --help, -h
    Show this help

  --version, -v
    Show version number
